PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA 14-year-old boy from West Sussex on
OL,8,Fa world voyage with his family died
OL,9,Fafter being struck by the propellers
OL,10,Fof a "fast-moving, unlicensed
OL,11,Fspeedboat" when he was snorkelling in
OL,12,Fthe South Pacific, an inquest has
OL,13,Fconcluded.
OL,15,FEddie Jarman, who grew up in West
OL,16,FHoathly, was hit in the head and chest
OL,17,Fby a three-tonne, semi-rigid
OL,18,Finflatable boat in Mo'orea Bay, near
OL,19,FTahiti in French Polynesia, on August
OL,20,F9 2020.
OL,26,@rD@FOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe British-Polish teenager had been
OL,8,Fon a round-the-world sailing trip with
OL,9,Fhis family and they had a few months
OL,10,Fleft of their adventures before
OL,11,Freturning to the UK.
OL,13,FHe had been snorkelling near his
OL,14,Ffamily's anchored boat facing the
OL,15,Fbeach when he was hit by a driver, a
OL,16,Flocal lagoon guide, who had rented the
OL,17,Fmore than five-metre vessel for the
OL,18,Fday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn evidence from Eddie's family, heard
OL,8,Fat an inquest on Tuesday, they said
OL,9,Fthey had been "fighting for justice
OL,10,Ffor a long and painful four years".
OL,12,FAn involuntary manslaughter
OL,13,Finvestigation was launched by local
OL,14,Fpolice following the incident but
OL,15,Fofficials did not bring any charges,
OL,16,Fdespite legal challenges by the
OL,17,Ffamily, the inquest heard.
OL,26,@qD@OOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAt the hearing at Woodvale Crematorium
OL,8,Fin Brighton, area coroner Joseph
OL,9,FTurner said despite Eddie being taken
OL,10,Fto shore and attempts to resuscitate
OL,11,Fhim, his injuries were likely to be
OL,12,F"immediately fatal and non survivable".
OL,14,FConflicting evidence was heard over
OL,15,Fthe speed of the boat that hit Eddie,
OL,16,Fincluding that Eddie's father, Harry
OL,17,FJarman, had told local police he had
OL,18,Fseen the man and woman "coming at full
OL,19,Fspeed behind us" and the driver was
OL,20,F"practically skimming" above the water.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@fO]zD@XOU{D@PO]|D@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Jarman had said he thought he was
OL,8,Fgoing "too fast and close", adding; "I
OL,9,Fturned around thinking he's crazy".
OL,11,FBut the driver had told officers he
OL,12,Fwas going under the 20-knot speed
OL,13,Flimit and argued he had adjusted his
OL,14,Fspeed while piloting in the channel.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@ZO]pD@eOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe coroner concluded it was likely
OL,8,Fthe boat was travelling within the
OL,9,Fspeed limit, but added: "In other
OL,10,Fparts of the world, in proximity to
OL,11,Fthat moored vessel and the beach would
OL,12,Fnot have a speed limit of 20 knots,
OL,13,Fbut that was the speed limit in place,
OL,14,Fat that place, at that time."
OL,26,@qD@YOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquest heard an involuntary
OL,8,Fmanslaughter investigation was opened
OL,9,Fby local authorities at the time of
OL,10,Fthe incident but a bid from a public
OL,11,Fprosecutor and the family to bring
OL,12,Fcharges was refused by the
OL,13,Finvestigating judge.
OL,15,FA subsequent appeal asked the initial
OL,16,Fjudge to reconsider but they continued
OL,17,Fto take the view there was not a
OL,18,F"realistic prospect of conviction
OL,19,Fbecause of the totality of evidence",
OL,20,Fthe coroner said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA further appeal to a higher court
OL,8,Falso agreed with the decision of the
OL,9,Ffirst judge, and a further legal
OL,10,Fchallenge to a higher court in Paris
OL,11,Funder the French legal system has not
OL,12,Fbeen pursued by the family at this
OL,13,Ftime, having been told they had
OL,14,F"limited prospect of success".
OL,16,FThe inquest heard that both the driver
OL,17,Fand his passenger confirmed before the
OL,18,Fincident they had been for lunch and
OL,19,Fshared a bottle of wine.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe driver also confirmed he had been
OL,8,Fdrinking alcohol the day before,
OL,9,Fhaving a party with other instructors
OL,10,Ffor the end of summer camp season.
OL,12,FBut toxicology samples taken from the
OL,13,Fdriver the day of the incident came
OL,14,Fback clear more than a month later,
OL,15,Fwith the family questioning the
OL,16,Fresults.
OL,18,FEddie's mother Barbara Genda told the
OL,19,Fcoroner: "To me there was no alcohol
OL,20,Fat all in results, no trace, it's
OL,21,Fpretty impossible."
OL,26,@{D@JOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn his summary of findings, coroner Mr
OL,8,FTurner also said: "The evidence is
OL,9,Fclear the boat driver and his
OL,10,Fcompanion had been up to probably the
OL,11,Fearly hours of the night before, they
OL,12,Fhad just come from lunch where they
OL,13,Fhad consumed wine.
OL,15,F"Samples taken proved negative for
OL,16,Falcohol and drugs, it is difficult for
OL,17,Fme to reconcile that evidence.
OL,26,@pD@SOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"It does seem more probable than not
OL,8,Fthere would have been some alcohol in
OL,9,Fhis system at the time from his own
OL,10,Fevidence."
OL,12,FBut the coroner added the driver of
OL,13,Fthe boat knew the area very well and
OL,14,Fwas experienced driving that type of
OL,15,Fvessel.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Turner told Eddie's parents that he
OL,8,Fwas unable to reach a conclusion of
OL,9,Funlawful killing as the circumstances
OL,10,Fof the driver did not meet all six
OL,11,Felements to meet that threshold,
OL,12,Finstead returning a narrative
OL,13,Fconclusion.
OL,15,FHe gave the court's sincere
OL,16,Fcondolences for the "unimaginable
OL,17,Ftragic loss of your young son".
OL,26,@xD@UOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777532747
OL,3,CBoy died snorkelling when he was hit
OL,4,Cby 'fast-moving' speedboat, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAt the time of Eddie's death, his
OL,8,Ffamily set up a crowdfunder for
OL,9,F#100,000 and set up a young musicians'
OL,10,Fcharity in his memory.
OL,12,FHis mother wrote on August 12 for the
OL,13,Ffundraiser, days after his death:
OL,14,F"Eddie loved music more than anything,
OL,15,Fhe often said that he could not
OL,16,Fimagine living without music, either
OL,17,Fplaying it or listening to it. In his
OL,18,Fmemory let other children enjoy music
OL,19,Fas much as he has in his short but
OL,20,Fwonderful life."
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
